org.contentmine.graphics.svg

Class GraphicsElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • nu.xom.Node
      • nu.xom.ParentNode
        • nu.xom.Element

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EuclidConstants, XMLConstants, SVGConstants
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SVGElement

    public class GraphicsElement
extends AbstractCMElement
implements SVGConstants
    Base class for lightweight generic SVG element. manages attributes (I think) No checking - i.e. can take any name or attributes. Note sure whether there is any real distinction between GraphicsElement and SVGElement
    Author:
    pm286
